                <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">Agentic Proposing：proposer pipeline。</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure class="card overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/notes/agentic-proposing-skillclaw/agentic-proposing-fig2-overall.png" alt="Agentic Proposing fig2" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/70" />
                <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">Agentic Proposing：overall。</figcaption>
