            <figure class="card overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/notes/agentic-proposing-skillclaw/agentic-proposing-fig3-accuracy.png" alt="Agentic Proposing fig3" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/70" />
                <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">Agentic Proposing：accuracy / results（裁剪图）。</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure class="card overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/notes/agentic-proposing-skillclaw/agentic-proposing-fig4-head.png" alt="Agentic Proposing fig4" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/70" />
                <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">Agentic Proposing：head / 结构图（裁剪图）。</figcaption>
            </figure>
